          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-copy-7-1680598832707-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> cooked lean beef mince</strong> to a bowl and reserve the pan</p><p>Peel and finely slice the<strong> brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat and once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-7 min or until softened and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
