    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> tomatoes</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>spring greens </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper  </p><p>Rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips </p>",
